root: ^!Well it seems as though both of our daughters are wonderful.
^!After Jade and I’s intense battle, Amelia and Lilith begin talking about their favorite bands, bonding over Amelia’s new vinyl.
^!Meanwhile, Jade and I sit on a bench outside of Gothic Glam and talk about our interests.
^!Jade seems very interested in the Victorian era, telling me fun facts about its history as I nod in interest.
^&Perhaps I could take you to my estate later, I believe it will be pleasurable for you.
^!I try to play off my excitement as I can’t wait to hangout more with Jade.
^!After a while of getting to know each other, I can’t help but feel as though Jade and I will be good friends.
^%We must depart as our meeting encroaches.
^%However, I frankly am quite excited to see you tonight.
^%Alright, hope everything goes well at your conference!
^!Amelia and I wave goodbye as Jade and Lilith exit the mall.
^%Alright Amelia, ready for our shitty mall pretzel!
